Famemonitor
========================
/(?<=Name:)(.*?)(?=<\/p>)/m.match(searchText) #name
/(?<=AKA:)(.*?)(?=<\/p>)/m.match(searchText) #AKA
/(?<=Born:)(.*?)(?=<\/p>)/m.match(searchText) # dob
/(?<=Birthplace:)(.*?)(?=<\/p>)/m.match(searchText) # birthplace
/(?<=Gender:)(.*?)(?=<\/p>)/m.match(searchText) # Gender
/(?<=Race:)(.*?)(?=<\/p>)/m.match(searchText) # Race
/(?<=Orientation:)(.*?)(?=<\/p>)/m.match(searchText) # sexual orientation
/(?<=Occupation:)(.*?)(?=<\/p>)/m.match(searchText) # occupation
/(?<=Affiliation:)(.*?)(?=<\/p>)/m.match(searchText) # political affiliation
/(?<=Nationality:)(.*?)(?=<\/p>)/m.match(searchText) # nationality
/(?<=Description:)(.*?)(?=<\/p>)/m.match(searchText) # known for

